  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink44-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">parattaiyar maṉaikkaṇṇē paṉṉāḷ taṅkit taṉmaṉaikkaṇṇē vanta talaimakaṟkut
          tōḻi kūṟiyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink44">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> tīmperum poykai yāmai yiḷampārpput</l>
          <l> tāymuka nōkki vaḷarntici ṉāaṅ</l>
          <l> katuvē yaiyaniṉ mārpē</l>
          <l> yaṟintaṉai yoḻukumati yaṟaṉumā ratuvē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

          <l> In the big, sweet pond </l>
          <l> the tender young of the tortoise </l>
          <l> growing by gazing into the faces of [their] mothers–</l>
          <l> That's exactly what your chest is like, o lord! </l>
          <l> You who know [this], act lawfully! That indeed is [your] duty. </l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
